&lt;h1 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;details&gt;
&lt;summary&gt;游戏概述&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In the year 2032, humanity stands on the brink of a technological breakthrough. A new material, developed by a group of scientists, possesses not only extraordinary strength, hyper-elasticity, and energy-saving properties, but also a unique, or rather exceptional, ability to self-repair. This capability turned the material into a regenerative pill, allowing people with limited abilities to become fully functional humans, while also making them stronger, smarter, and even extending their lifespan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;details&gt;
&lt;summary&gt;Spoiler: More&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;However, fearing the consequences of such power, the scientists decide to destroy the records, reports, and everything related to their research. They scattered, each going their own way. But as is often the case, someone found the remnants of this work. Ignoring the dangers, they decided to complete it, which eventually led to the formation of a globally banned terrorist organization called &amp;ldquo;Masquerade.&amp;rdquo; In response, leaders of major corporations launched a large-scale operation to eliminate the individual responsible and eradicate everything related to the research.
You are a former soldier, unable to bear the guilt of the atrocities committed during the operation. You retreat to a remote location on the edge of the world, a small town cut off from the rest of civilization, where you planned to live a peaceful life with your wife and children, far removed from all the troubles of the past.
But, as often happens, things do not go according to plan. One day, when your wife goes on a business trip to a certain research institute, she suddenly stops contacting you. In an attempt to find out what happened, you embark on a journey. Days, weeks, months, and years pass&amp;hellip; Eventually, you come to terms with the fact that you may never see your wife again, burying all your emotions deep inside. Then, one day, your son arrives, asking for your help and with a glimmer of hope that not all is lost, that there is still a small chance to restore your peaceful life.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;
